        "data": {
            "requirement": "You have come into contact with the Gift Spirit.",
            "effect": "By calming your mind and concentrating, you can open your mind to the spiritual world and communicate with restless souls. Spend 1 Soma to contact a creature with the Spirit Gift you’ve previously encountered. You do not suffer the Wound caused by the stress of spiritual connection."
